<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=2121&amp;p=17948#p17948"><![CDATA[
The only heat you'll find will be on the voltage regulator/it's heat sink. If you want to do away with heat, get a better regulator which doesn't need a heat sink or get a gigantic fin heatsink. A fan on a NES would be sad, not cool.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=20">kyuusaku</a> — Sat Sep 23, 2006 2:56 pm</p><hr />
